AI is reshaping business, and Salesforce is leading the way with record-breaking momentum. We just delivered our highest revenue, operating margin, and cash flow in company history — driving a $37.9 billion year and our first-ever $10 billion quarter. But what’s ahead is even bigger. The rise of the AI-powered workforce has unlocked a multi- trillion-dollar market. And with Agentforce — the first digital labor platform for enterprises — we’re redefining how work gets done. Thousands of companies are already seeing transformational results, and this is just the beginning. Our ecosystem is quickly expanding, fueled by Data Cloud, AgentExchange, and a growing community of 19 million Trailblazers. As always, we’re driving customer success while staying true to our core values. The future of AI isn’t coming, it’s here. And Salesforce is at the forefront of this revolution,
